Name: High Snack
Review Text: Best Snackbar in Amsterdam, had one of the best crispy chicken wrap ever!! The guy working there is just the best..friendly, helpful and overall great service! 10/10 would recommend to anyone wanting to stop by for a quick snack with their friends!!
